Package: qli
Title: Estimate Quantile LOWESS Intervals for Linear Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Martina", "Sladekova", , "m.sladekova@sussex.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5059-6576"))
Description: This package contains functions for applying a method described in Sladekova & Field (2024, https://doi.org/10.31234/osf.io/gn4mr) for quantifying heteroscedasticity in linear models using Quantile LOWESS Intervals.
